import numpy as np
import cv2
from typing import List

def minimum_enclosing_circle_radius_comparison(contour1: List[List[int]], contour2: List[List[int]]) -> float:
    (x1, y1), radius1 = cv2.minEnclosingCircle(np.array(contour1))
    (x2, y2), radius2 = cv2.minEnclosingCircle(np.array(contour2))
    return abs(radius1 - radius2)
